<h1>About App</h1>

<p><strong>App Name:</strong> SignalForge: Trading Signals</p>

<p><strong>Version:</strong> 1.0</p>

<p>
SignalForge: Trading Signals is a modern trading signal application designed to provide educational market insights, crypto alerts, forex updates, and trading notifications in a clean and user-friendly experience.
</p>

<h2>Features</h2>

<ul>
<li>Live Buy/Sell trading signals</li>
<li>Crypto market alerts</li>
<li>Forex signal updates</li>
<li>Real-time notifications</li>
<li>Simple and modern interface</li>
<li>Fast and lightweight performance</li>
</ul>

<h2>Purpose of the App</h2>

<p>
The purpose of SignalForge: Trading Signals is to help users stay informed about market movements and trading opportunities for educational and informational purposes only.
</p>

<h2>Important Notice</h2>

<p>
SignalForge: Trading Signals does not provide financial or investment advice.
</p>

<p>
Trading cryptocurrencies, forex, and financial markets involves risk. Users are responsible for their own trading decisions and financial activities.
</p>

<h2>Technology Used</h2>

<ul>
<li>Firebase Services</li>
<li>Google AdMob</li>
<li>Push Notifications</li>
<li>Modern Mobile UI</li>
</ul>

